  "1031140": {
    "name": "战锤 — 霍拉斯叛乱：军团",
    "steam_appid": 1031140,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一款基于《Warhammer：霍拉斯叛乱》的残暴卡牌游戏！</strong></h2>进入黑暗时代！拿起你的爆弹枪，组建一个无人可挡的卡组，并参与令人类帝国陷入动荡的内战。集齐这个时代的主要军队，从星际战士军团到火星部队和混沌爪牙，每个都拥有自身的独特机制与战斗风格。在你前往泰拉的旅程中，参与霍拉斯叛乱中最重要的几场战斗。你的行动会决定游戏的演变，所以为创造历史做好吧！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>========================= 游戏机制 =========================</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >从 100 多位传奇战将中选择</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/2c31c4c979ac99ce81b4f30c99a00c9c.poster.avif?t=1763035491\" width=610 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/2c31c4c979ac99ce81b4f30c99a00c9c.webm?t=1763035491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/2c31c4c979ac99ce81b4f30c99a00c9c.mp4?t=1763035491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你的战将冲锋在前，引领你的军队。数十个可供选择的战将，各有各的独特能力、特殊卡片以及戏剧性语音台词。你挑选的战将会决定你可有的选择，影响你的战略和胜利之路。你会保持忠诚，保卫人类帝国，还是会加入战帅的反叛大军？选择你的忠臣义士！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >为你的军队组成最强卡组</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/8062f0f3a2afdab1ac5396e824c2f823.poster.avif?t=1763035491\" width=610 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/8062f0f3a2afdab1ac5396e824c2f823.webm?t=1763035491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/8062f0f3a2afdab1ac5396e824c2f823.mp4?t=1763035491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>从霍拉斯叛乱的所有主要阵营中选择你喜欢的军队。探索形形色色的阿斯塔特军团，为帝国而战的禁卫军和寂静修女，机械神的骑士团及其他仆人，以及毁灭风暴的恶魔和其他混沌爪牙。欣赏令人惊叹的艺术作品。有超过1,300张卡牌可供选择，可能性无穷无尽！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌握深层机制，适用每个兵种的特长</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/4db18795fe8d3e4bc2d14b8bb3f67119.poster.avif?t=1763035491\" width=610 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/4db18795fe8d3e4bc2d14b8bb3f67119.webm?t=1763035491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/4db18795fe8d3e4bc2d14b8bb3f67119.mp4?t=1763035491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>每个兵种都其独特的特征，代表其独特的战争方式。从皇嗣们在寻求完美回合时运用的复杂战术，到吞世者们的直接、血腥的战法，每场对决都有自己的不同故事。找到适合自己风格的战法！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>========================== 游戏模式 ==========================</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >排名模式：你能成为战帅吗？</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/fd00ed83209ad919cffd465218ad0004.poster.avif?t=1763035491\" width=610 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/fd00ed83209ad919cffd465218ad0004.webm?t=1763035491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/fd00ed83209ad919cffd465218ad0004.mp4?t=1763035491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>通过霍拉斯叛乱的主要战场，从伊斯塔万到卡尔斯一路晋升。最后，到达泰拉，为成为战帅而战！在月度赛季中证明自己的战力，赢得大量奖励及独家卡背，以展示自己的统治力。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >单人游戏战役：深入剧情，开始收集</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/58e42bd87242b7b711c803afd532834c.poster.avif?t=1763035491\" width=610 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/58e42bd87242b7b711c803afd532834c.webm?t=1763035491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/58e42bd87242b7b711c803afd532834c.mp4?t=1763035491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>重温畅销小说中的关键战役，并在银河系中忠臣和叛徒的主要冲突中证明自己。以一组15张牌开局，面对难度不断增加的一系列敌人。随着一路解锁新战将、卡牌及升级物品，做好面对史诗级最终敌人的准备！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选秀模式：以故事中著名战役为基础的限时竞技场</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/eb4b4acd5b11dd37d73d3d4f824d94e2.poster.avif?t=1763035491\" width=610 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/eb4b4acd5b11dd37d73d3d4f824d94e2.webm?t=1763035491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/eb4b4acd5b11dd37d73d3d4f824d94e2.mp4?t=1763035491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在基于霍拉斯叛乱主要战役的限时场景中证明你的选秀能力。每个活动都有不同的战将，包括活动专属战将。赚取个人奖励，并帮助你的公会在活动排行榜上独占鳌头!此外，取决于你扮演的战将，你的胜利会给忠臣或叛徒带来积分。每场活动的结果决定了哪些新内容会被添加到游戏中！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>=================== 更多惊艳特色 ===================</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与其他玩家一起加入公会</h2>通过公会系统与来自银河系各地的玩家组队。享用私密聊天室，分享卡组列表、策略建议并玩练习赛，从而为战斗做好准备。在活动的排行榜上名列前茅，赢取丰富奖励，并参加社区领导的公会锦标赛！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >桌面及移动系统之间的完全跨平台能力</h2>注册你的账户，在多个设备之间无缝游戏。在家里享受长时间连续多场竞技比赛，或者在途中从你的移动设备介入快速练习比赛。能够随身携带你的全部收集及进展<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/3b01096be595a009df6bad15ce320921.poster.avif?t=1763035491\" width=610 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/3b01096be595a009df6bad15ce320921.webm?t=1763035491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/3b01096be595a009df6bad15ce320921.mp4?t=1763035491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全星系沟通</h2>加入全局聊天室，与整个银河系的所有其他玩家交流。点击任何信息都会自动翻译成你自己的语言，让你与人类和异族人交流。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无尽的成就与挑战</h2>有数以百计的里程碑和成就需要完成，指导你通过游戏的早期阶段，并为包括最资深在内的所有玩家提供长期目标。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/799db80ab7e0273ca4520aa1930b9b8b.poster.avif?t=1763035491\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/799db80ab7e0273ca4520aa1930b9b8b.webm?t=1763035491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1031140/extras/799db80ab7e0273ca4520aa1930b9b8b.mp4?t=1763035491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
